          <h3 class="text-center" id="pg1"> Guestbook</h3>
          <br>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
            <h4>Description</h4>
            <p>
              The MAZI Guestbook is an open source application that can used in events enabling the audience to share their thoughts, photos, etc.
            </p>

            <h4>Administration Guide</h4>
            <p>
              To configure/moderate the MAZI Guestbook application, you can go to <a target="_blank" href="http://portal.mazizone.eu/admin_guestbook" class="app-link" >portal.mazizone.eu/admin_guestbook</a>.
            </p>

            <h4>Admin Password</h4>
            <p>
              In order to change the admin password, open the config.js file ,which takes place in this path: <b>/var/www/html/mazi-board/src/node/config.js</b>, and then fill the authPassword with the password you like.
            </p>
            <pre><code>
              /* AUTH DATA */
              authName: 'admin',
              authPassword: 'password',
            </code></pre>

            <h4>Alternative views of content</h4>
            <p>
              As well as standard web browser presentation of content, GuestBook supports two other views of content
            </p>
            <p><b>Slideshow view:</b> <a href="http://portal.mazizone.eu:8081/#projection" target='_blank'>http://portal.mazizone.eu:8081/#projection</a> *</p>
            <p><b>Tablet view:</b> <a href="http://portal.mazizone.eu:8081/#tablet" target='_blank'>http://portal.mazizone.eu:8081/#tablet</a> *</p>
            <p>* all links work when you are connected to your MAZI Zone.</p>
